flowchart LR
  %% Diagram 34A: AI Intelligence Business-Friendly Cycle

  Data[Business data\nsales + inventory + festivals + weather] --> Forecast[AI predicts near-term demand]
  Forecast --> Insights[Platform creates clear insights\nrestock, discount, bundle, pricing]
  Insights --> WhatIf[Vendor explores What-If scenarios\nadjust price, festival, weather sliders\nsee impact before deciding]
  WhatIf --> Advisor[Sahayak explains actions\nin Bangla/English]
  Advisor --> Decision{Vendor approves action?}

  Decision -- Yes --> Execute[Platform executes approved actions]
  Decision -- No --> Observe[Keep monitoring and suggest alternatives]

  Execute --> Results[Track outcomes\nsales, stock health, fulfillment quality]
  Observe --> Results

  Results --> Feedback[Weekly feedback loop\ncompare prediction vs actual]
  Feedback --> Improve[Model improves or safely falls back]
  Improve --> Forecast

  Guard1[Privacy guard\nCross-vendor analytics require >= 3 vendors]
  Guard2[Safety guard\nNo irreversible mutation without confirmation]

  Guard1 -.applies to.-> Insights
  Guard2 -.applies to.-> Decision
